<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh nangmah ka keng tuah, A sungmi na thi in, Mi vialte an thian
 khawhnak, Kalvary tlang in a luang.

[C1]
   Vailam ah, Vailam ah, Ka lianhnak si ko seh, Ka thlarau vangcung
   khua ah, Lungdainak phan ko seh.

[V2]
 Vailam pawngah ther pah in, Dawt hramhnak kha ka hmuh, Zinglei deirel
 arfi nih, Ka velchum a run ceuh.

[C2]
   Vailam ah, Vailam ah, Ka lianhnak si ko seh, Ka thlarau vangcung
   khua ah, Lungdainak phan ko seh.

[V3]
 Pathian tuufa vailam ah, Na huahnak ka hngalhter, A thladem in nifate,
 Him in ka huppheng ko.

[C3]
   Vailam ah, Vailam ah, Ka lianhnak si ko seh, Ka thlarau vangcung
   khua ah, Lungdainak phan ko seh.

[V4]
 Vailam pawngin ka hngah lai, Zumh le ruahchannak he, Hmun dawhbik ka
 phak hlan tiang, Tiva ral sui khua cu.

[C4]
   Vailam ah, Vailam ah, Ka lianhnak si ko seh, Ka thlarau vangcung
   khua ah, Lungdainak phan ko seh.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>VAILAM PAWNGAH CH120</title>
<hymn_number>120</hymn_number>
</song>